## Mechanical Indicators

The following mechanical events occurred this turn.  You MAY place each
marker inside your narration at the narratively appropriate point —
typically immediately before describing the consequence of that event.

Place each marker on its own line, surrounded by blank lines (`\n\n`),
like this:

```
You try to lift the statue.

[MECH:check:0]

It's too heavy to budge.
```

If you do not use a marker, the engine will prepend it to your narration
automatically.  Use each marker at most once.

{% if indicators %}
{% for ind in indicators %}
- `{{ ind.marker }}` — {{ ind.plain_description }}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
_There are no mechanical indicators for this turn._
{% endif %}

